PrecisApproval of the variation made to Licence No. GL-157 issued to SELKIRK COGEN PARTNERS, L.P. by the National Energy Board for the exportation of natural gas to the U.S., in order to allow its gas to be exported from a point situated near Niagara Falls, Ontario, as well as from Iroquois, Ontario (N.E.B.
